WEBVTT

00:00:20.875 --> 00:00:21.709
Hey.

00:00:22.210 --> 00:00:23.837
What are you still doing here?

00:00:24.796 --> 00:00:28.049
I'm sorry. I thought you were my friend.

00:00:28.133 --> 00:00:30.218
Let's go. Everyone's here.

00:00:33.054 --> 00:00:35.515
Wait. Why is he leaving?

00:00:37.642 --> 00:00:38.726
So it wasn't him?

00:00:39.727 --> 00:00:42.689
Mi-rae!

00:00:43.273 --> 00:00:44.566
Ms. Choi?

00:00:45.984 --> 00:00:47.777
Su-ji, a college friend.

00:00:47.861 --> 00:00:49.154
What?

00:00:49.988 --> 00:00:52.490
The campus is so big. I still get lost.

00:00:52.574 --> 00:00:55.243
I almost lost you on my way back
from the bathroom.

00:00:55.326 --> 00:00:56.161
Let's go!

00:00:56.828 --> 00:00:57.662
Go where?

00:00:57.745 --> 00:01:00.290
What? We said we would go together.

00:01:01.499 --> 00:01:02.584
Over there.

00:01:05.420 --> 00:01:08.256
Yay, we're here!

00:01:08.339 --> 00:01:09.632
Isn't it great?

00:01:09.716 --> 00:01:10.884
"Freshmen"?

00:01:10.967 --> 00:01:12.135
WELCOME, FRESHMEN!

00:01:12.218 --> 00:01:15.263
I'm not a freshman, am I?

00:01:15.346 --> 00:01:16.514
No way.

00:01:16.598 --> 00:01:17.599
How much is this?

00:01:17.682 --> 00:01:18.641
STUDENT COUNCIL

00:01:18.725 --> 00:01:21.311
It's so pretty. Can I have this?

00:01:21.811 --> 00:01:22.645
Thank you!

00:01:23.980 --> 00:01:25.190
-You there!
-I got this.

00:01:25.273 --> 00:01:26.274
Freshmen!

00:01:49.756 --> 00:01:51.424
You gotta be shitting me.

00:01:57.889 --> 00:01:59.849
Let's go. That's awful.

00:01:59.933 --> 00:02:01.559
Join us in the near future.

00:02:01.643 --> 00:02:02.518
Never.

00:02:02.602 --> 00:02:03.728
Not you!

00:02:03.811 --> 00:02:04.812
Go away!

00:02:05.855 --> 00:02:06.731
Take a look.

00:02:06.814 --> 00:02:08.107
Check it out. It's fun.

00:02:08.191 --> 00:02:09.651
Come check us out.

00:02:09.734 --> 00:02:11.444
-This way!
-Come this way.

00:02:11.527 --> 00:02:15.114
-Take a quick look.
-Check out what we're all about.

00:02:16.824 --> 00:02:18.534
-We have cameras.
-Show us your kicks!

00:02:18.618 --> 00:02:20.745
-We're offering free photos!
-Free pictures!

00:02:20.828 --> 00:02:23.248
Why is this line so long, Ms. Choi?

00:02:23.331 --> 00:02:24.332
Hey!

00:02:24.415 --> 00:02:27.293
Don't call me that.
You're weirding me out.

00:02:29.504 --> 00:02:32.382
I know, right? Girl, that was so weird!

00:02:33.758 --> 00:02:37.428
They must be lining up to get tickets
for the kumdo match today.

00:02:37.512 --> 00:02:40.473
I heard in the bathroom earlier
that it was sold out.

00:02:40.556 --> 00:02:42.850
Are they waiting
to get canceled tickets or what?

00:02:42.934 --> 00:02:45.270
The kumdo club must be really popular.

00:02:46.437 --> 00:02:49.941
I heard it's even more popular
than the soccer and hockey teams here.

00:02:51.776 --> 00:02:53.903
No way! You got tickets?

00:02:53.987 --> 00:02:56.239
Where did you get these? That's insane!

00:02:56.322 --> 00:02:58.199
I'm supposed to go here, aren't I?

00:02:59.117 --> 00:03:00.493
You have to go.

00:03:01.536 --> 00:03:02.537
Come along now.

00:03:02.620 --> 00:03:03.955
It's this way.

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:23.725
He's here!

00:03:23.808 --> 00:03:25.435
13TH KUMDO FRIENDLY
HANSAE VS KOSAN

00:03:26.811 --> 00:03:28.062
What's going on?

00:03:28.730 --> 00:03:30.648
Didn't I tell you not to stand here?

00:03:30.732 --> 00:03:31.983
Why not?

00:03:32.066 --> 00:03:33.735
You're blocking the view!

00:03:33.818 --> 00:03:35.737
-Damn it!
-What did you say?

00:03:36.362 --> 00:03:39.324
Who are they?
Part of a fan club or something?

00:03:39.407 --> 00:03:40.241
I guess so.

00:03:40.325 --> 00:03:43.453
The Hansae-Kosan kumdo friendly match
will begin soon.

00:03:43.536 --> 00:03:46.664
Hansae University!

00:03:46.748 --> 00:03:48.041
EUN-HO, WE LOVE YOU

00:03:48.124 --> 00:03:51.711
Hansae University!

00:03:51.794 --> 00:03:55.048
-Hansae University!
-Kosan University!

00:03:55.131 --> 00:03:55.965
Begin!

00:03:59.469 --> 00:04:01.346
Head strike!

00:04:20.531 --> 00:04:24.619
-Seo Eun-ho of Hansae University has won.
-Eun-ho!

00:04:24.702 --> 00:04:28.664
In the next match,
Park Myeong-seong of Hansae University

00:04:28.748 --> 00:04:31.918
will be facing
An Hong-mo of Kosan University.

00:04:32.001 --> 00:04:33.669
Please remain seated.

00:04:48.559 --> 00:04:50.520
So cool!

00:04:50.603 --> 00:04:52.438
He's amazing.

00:05:06.244 --> 00:05:10.123
Congratulations, Ms. Seo Mi-rae,
on meeting your second date!

00:05:20.508 --> 00:05:21.551
I knew it.

00:05:22.343 --> 00:05:23.553
It was you.

00:05:30.143 --> 00:05:33.938
EPISODE 3
FIRST LOVE 101

00:05:37.108 --> 00:05:38.109
HANSAE KUMDO CLUB

00:05:38.192 --> 00:05:40.528
Are you guys joining because of Eun-ho?

00:05:40.611 --> 00:05:41.446
No.

00:05:42.697 --> 00:05:45.283
It's okay. That's why we joined too.

00:05:45.783 --> 00:05:48.703
-You want to get to know him better, huh?
-Yes!

00:05:49.662 --> 00:05:51.747
Then you'll have to get past us first.

00:05:57.044 --> 00:05:59.422
Is Seo Eun-ho really that popular?

00:06:00.214 --> 00:06:01.841
How could he not be?

00:06:01.924 --> 00:06:04.469
I'll bet all the girls here
wish he'd go on

00:06:04.552 --> 00:06:08.306
to earn his master's and doctorate
and become a professor here.

00:06:08.806 --> 00:06:11.267
Good thing the architecture program
is five years long.

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:12.393
He's not a PE major?

00:06:12.477 --> 00:06:15.480
Wow, he's in architecture.
He must be smart too.

00:06:16.063 --> 00:06:19.734
Eun-ho's good enough to run a country,
not just a company!

00:06:19.817 --> 00:06:21.277
Totally!

00:06:21.861 --> 00:06:25.031
So the most popular guy on campus
likes me?

00:06:26.824 --> 00:06:28.034
That's a decent plot.

00:06:28.117 --> 00:06:30.119
-Why are you laughing?
-What?

00:06:32.788 --> 00:06:34.165
It's nothing.

00:06:37.835 --> 00:06:39.045
Introduce myself?

00:06:42.882 --> 00:06:46.177
I'm Seo Mi-rae, a freshman.
Looking forward to it.

00:06:55.728 --> 00:06:56.979
Where am I now?

00:06:58.856 --> 00:07:00.149
He's so handsome.

00:07:00.233 --> 00:07:03.319
All right, freshmen.
It's our first time seeing each other.

00:07:03.819 --> 00:07:04.654
Say hello.

00:07:04.737 --> 00:07:08.282
-Hello.
-Hello.

00:07:11.619 --> 00:07:12.703
Hey.

00:07:12.787 --> 00:07:14.163
What are you still doing here?

00:07:16.249 --> 00:07:18.417
It's the girl I saw earlier.

00:07:18.501 --> 00:07:21.254
Hey, isn't the club president
just gorgeous?

00:07:23.089 --> 00:07:24.090
She is.

00:07:41.691 --> 00:07:45.319
Kumdo is the best sport
for training one's body and mind.

00:07:45.403 --> 00:07:50.283
We will help you enjoy every aspect of it,
from the basic stances to sparring.

00:07:50.783 --> 00:07:54.453
Since it's your first day,
let's start with the basic footwork.

00:07:55.454 --> 00:07:56.664
Any volunteers?

00:07:57.373 --> 00:07:58.791
Who wants to give it a go?

00:08:07.592 --> 00:08:09.510
Good. Come on out, then.

00:08:10.094 --> 00:08:10.928
Sorry?

00:08:13.723 --> 00:08:14.849
No, I'm good.

00:08:14.932 --> 00:08:16.309
Come out. It's okay.

00:08:16.392 --> 00:08:17.268
Get out there.

00:08:22.148 --> 00:08:23.482
What was your name again?

00:08:23.566 --> 00:08:25.985
It's Seo Mi-rae.

00:08:32.491 --> 00:08:35.911
It would be nice
if someone could help out.

00:08:38.456 --> 00:08:40.291
All right. Help us, will you?

00:08:40.374 --> 00:08:43.044
They probably all came to see you anyway.

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:45.713
Shall I?

00:08:49.091 --> 00:08:50.301
Is that okay with you?

00:08:52.094 --> 00:08:52.928
Yes.

00:08:59.977 --> 00:09:00.811
Hi.

00:09:02.271 --> 00:09:03.773
Hello.

00:09:03.856 --> 00:09:05.399
Have you tried kumdo before?

00:09:06.776 --> 00:09:07.943
No, I haven't.

00:09:13.366 --> 00:09:14.200
Here.

00:09:17.036 --> 00:09:18.371
Hold it like this.

00:09:19.497 --> 00:09:21.040
Right foot, forward.

00:09:24.126 --> 00:09:25.586
How is it? Comfortable?

00:09:26.837 --> 00:09:27.672
Yes.

00:09:29.423 --> 00:09:30.508
High stance.

00:09:32.343 --> 00:09:33.344
Head strike.

00:09:33.427 --> 00:09:35.137
And this is the middle stance,

00:09:35.763 --> 00:09:37.848
which will be your basic stance.

00:09:37.932 --> 00:09:38.974
Want to give it a go?

00:09:40.309 --> 00:09:41.143
Yes.

00:09:47.358 --> 00:09:48.192
Go ahead.

00:09:50.611 --> 00:09:51.445
Head strike.

00:10:00.037 --> 00:10:01.330
What was that?

00:10:02.331 --> 00:10:03.916
Is this really your first time?

00:10:03.999 --> 00:10:06.168
This is my first time.

00:10:07.545 --> 00:10:11.632
What just happened?
I usually have two left feet.

00:10:13.843 --> 00:10:17.138
You're really athletic, huh?
Let's try that again.

00:10:19.056 --> 00:10:19.890
Okay.

00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:02.600
Wasn't she a blur just now?
What did I just see?

00:11:03.100 --> 00:11:04.393
No way.

00:11:04.894 --> 00:11:06.771
Mi-rae, you've really got talent.

00:11:07.521 --> 00:11:09.940
Come on.
Eun-ho was obviously going easy on her.

00:11:10.024 --> 00:11:10.983
I wasn't.

00:11:12.234 --> 00:11:13.611
Great job.

00:11:14.987 --> 00:11:16.363
I'll be looking forward to it.

00:11:18.783 --> 00:11:19.617
Okay.

00:11:21.243 --> 00:11:23.287
-Head strike!
-Head strike.

00:11:23.370 --> 00:11:25.456
-He's just so cool.
-One.

00:11:25.956 --> 00:11:27.291
-I know!
-Head strike.

00:11:27.374 --> 00:11:29.293
-Look how stable he is.
-Middle stance.

00:11:29.376 --> 00:11:31.879
He's just so insanely buff!

00:11:31.962 --> 00:11:33.130
You know it!

00:11:33.923 --> 00:11:35.466
Like you're walking. Watch me.

00:11:35.549 --> 00:11:36.425
One!

00:11:36.509 --> 00:11:37.468
Head strike!

00:11:38.344 --> 00:11:39.512
Very good.

00:11:41.138 --> 00:11:42.515
Mr. Ko?

00:11:51.649 --> 00:11:54.527
Why are you guys just standing here?
Is something wrong?

00:11:55.820 --> 00:11:57.446
Jung-pil, kumdo club senior.

00:11:58.113 --> 00:11:59.114
Actually…

00:11:59.990 --> 00:12:00.825
What's your name?

00:12:02.284 --> 00:12:03.452
-It's Su-ji.
-Su-ji?

00:12:03.536 --> 00:12:04.954
-Yes.
-Su-ji, come over here.

00:12:05.037 --> 00:12:05.913
Okay.

00:12:06.455 --> 00:12:09.667
-The key to kumdo is smooth movement.
-Okay.

00:12:09.750 --> 00:12:10.876
Head strike!

00:12:11.627 --> 00:12:12.545
Head strike!

00:12:12.628 --> 00:12:14.338
That was so smooth.

00:12:14.421 --> 00:12:15.422
You try.

00:12:17.466 --> 00:12:18.634
Head strike!

00:12:19.134 --> 00:12:21.011
Hey, keep an eye on everyone.

00:12:21.095 --> 00:12:22.263
Sure.

00:12:22.346 --> 00:12:23.597
Head strike!

00:12:27.852 --> 00:12:28.686
Eun-ho.

00:12:31.689 --> 00:12:34.483
-Where are you off to?
-The library. Why do you ask?

00:12:35.943 --> 00:12:38.028
Would you like to have lunch with me?

00:12:39.196 --> 00:12:40.155
All together?

00:12:41.866 --> 00:12:42.700
No.

00:12:43.784 --> 00:12:45.035
Just the two of us?

00:12:45.703 --> 00:12:46.537
Yes.

00:12:49.915 --> 00:12:51.417
You're quite impatient, huh?

00:12:53.168 --> 00:12:55.421
Next time, once we know each other better.

00:12:56.297 --> 00:12:57.715
-What?
-Take care.

00:12:59.341 --> 00:13:00.968
Eun-ho?

00:13:01.051 --> 00:13:02.136
Hey, Eun-ho!

00:13:03.637 --> 00:13:05.306
Where are you going? Let me come.

00:13:05.389 --> 00:13:06.307
Let's go eat.

00:13:11.520 --> 00:13:13.522
Weren't you supposed to have
fallen for me?

00:13:13.606 --> 00:13:14.982
Why should he?

00:13:15.065 --> 00:13:18.110
He should be into me.
This is Boyfriend on Demand, after all.

00:13:18.611 --> 00:13:21.530
I think you may have gotten
the wrong idea.

00:13:21.614 --> 00:13:22.448
Wrong idea?

00:13:23.407 --> 00:13:27.912
Did you think that all 900 guys here
would be chasing after you from the start?

00:13:29.705 --> 00:13:31.373
But…

00:13:35.252 --> 00:13:36.754
Choi Si-woo liked me from the--

00:13:36.837 --> 00:13:40.174
That's just how that scenario was written.

00:13:43.260 --> 00:13:44.094
SPRING, AND YOU

00:13:44.178 --> 00:13:47.097
You don't look it, but you've got
a pretty bad princess complex.

00:13:47.932 --> 00:13:51.644
Are you saying Seo Eun-ho
might not ever end up falling for me?

00:13:51.727 --> 00:13:55.648
There's no telling that.
Some dates are more difficult than others.

00:13:56.357 --> 00:13:59.944
If I have to work for it,
how's it any different from reality?

00:14:00.027 --> 00:14:03.364
Would you rather date another guy?
Shall we move on?

00:14:07.785 --> 00:14:09.370
No, wait. Hey!

00:14:09.453 --> 00:14:10.454
Hold on a second.

00:14:10.537 --> 00:14:13.874
If you're not feeling it, just move on.
You don't have much time.

00:14:13.958 --> 00:14:15.876
I know. My time…

00:14:16.877 --> 00:14:17.711
Time?

00:14:30.099 --> 00:14:30.933
Jesus.

00:14:44.154 --> 00:14:45.364
Kyeong-nam.

00:14:46.740 --> 00:14:47.741
Man, look at her.

00:14:51.495 --> 00:14:52.413
You want coffee?

00:14:52.496 --> 00:14:55.290
PlanC had a decent first episode as well.

00:15:00.629 --> 00:15:02.089
But Yun Song's tough, right?

00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:04.842
I knew what we were up against.

00:15:05.426 --> 00:15:08.095
Did you really ask to be moved to Fridays?

00:15:08.178 --> 00:15:09.013
No.

00:15:10.639 --> 00:15:12.099
Ms. Seo didn't seem to think so.

00:15:12.683 --> 00:15:14.935
Obviously. She doesn't like me, after all.

00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:17.396
Don't you?

00:15:27.614 --> 00:15:28.449
What?

00:15:29.992 --> 00:15:30.951
Yes?

00:15:32.661 --> 00:15:33.495
Come in.

00:15:37.875 --> 00:15:39.334
Did you want to see me?

00:15:41.086 --> 00:15:43.005
I just got off a call with Yun Song.

00:15:43.505 --> 00:15:44.965
What? What was it about?

00:15:45.049 --> 00:15:47.551
What else would that woman call me for?

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:51.847
Honestly, I want to end this series.

00:15:51.930 --> 00:15:53.474
I'm so sick and tired of it!

00:15:53.557 --> 00:15:55.976
Please save me.

00:15:59.980 --> 00:16:03.108
You don't mean
she's thinking about quitting?

00:16:03.192 --> 00:16:04.735
-She said she's quitting?
-What?

00:16:04.818 --> 00:16:06.528
-What?
-No.

00:16:06.612 --> 00:16:07.571
Damn it.

00:16:08.322 --> 00:16:09.364
Then why did she…

00:16:10.574 --> 00:16:13.994
She wants two weeks off.
Otherwise, we'll be attending her funeral.

00:16:14.870 --> 00:16:17.331
Ms. Yun has been through a lot recently.

00:16:18.874 --> 00:16:19.708
Great work.

00:16:21.043 --> 00:16:23.670
-Sorry?
-I liked it. Keep it up.

00:16:24.463 --> 00:16:27.174
-I don't get why you were whining so much.
-Please…

00:16:27.257 --> 00:16:30.427
While Yun is on her break,
think about the next episodes.

00:16:32.096 --> 00:16:34.139
You approved her break?

00:16:35.933 --> 00:16:37.601
Seo Mi-rae is free on a weekday?

00:16:37.684 --> 00:16:39.520
It smells so good. Hurry up.

00:16:41.355 --> 00:16:45.359
So you'll be free for two weeks.
Should we go to Jeju over the weekend?

00:16:45.442 --> 00:16:47.569
Jeju? Don't even think about it.

00:16:47.653 --> 00:16:49.988
I have other authors to take care of.

00:16:51.281 --> 00:16:55.244
I've always thought that being a producer
is not worth the grind.

00:16:55.327 --> 00:16:56.495
Not worth it at all!

00:16:57.454 --> 00:16:59.373
It looks so good!

00:17:01.750 --> 00:17:02.584
Hey, Ji-yeon.

00:17:03.085 --> 00:17:08.423
Say you could go back to being 20.
What would you want to try?

00:17:13.053 --> 00:17:13.887
Sex.

00:17:16.431 --> 00:17:17.641
Not that kind of stuff!

00:17:19.685 --> 00:17:22.813
What's this out of the blue?
What would you do if you went back?

00:17:24.481 --> 00:17:27.985
I'd want my life to be
completely different from this one.

00:17:28.068 --> 00:17:29.153
The exact opposite.

00:17:29.236 --> 00:17:31.196
-The opposite?
-Yeah.

00:17:31.280 --> 00:17:35.033
You know, if I fell for someone,
I'd just go straight for him.

00:17:35.117 --> 00:17:36.493
Come what may,

00:17:37.119 --> 00:17:41.206
I'd be way more proactive
about pretty much everything.

00:17:43.834 --> 00:17:46.795
Hey, you're cracking me up!

00:17:46.879 --> 00:17:47.838
What's so funny?

00:17:47.921 --> 00:17:51.133
You were super proactive when you were 20.

00:17:51.216 --> 00:17:52.092
I was?

00:17:52.176 --> 00:17:53.260
Yes!

00:17:54.761 --> 00:17:56.930
Se-june had a crush on You-mi,

00:17:57.014 --> 00:18:00.350
and you kept trying to win him over
until you made him yours.

00:18:02.019 --> 00:18:04.021
You forgot, didn't you?

00:18:05.397 --> 00:18:08.483
You-mi sure was popular back in the day.

00:18:09.234 --> 00:18:11.445
Not as popular as me, but still.

00:18:13.614 --> 00:18:16.408
You're right. I was like that.

00:18:19.912 --> 00:18:21.496
So how did I end up like this?

00:18:22.539 --> 00:18:25.709
I guess dating him for too long
changed you.

00:18:26.293 --> 00:18:27.377
And you got older.

00:18:27.961 --> 00:18:29.338
I feel like

00:18:30.130 --> 00:18:32.716
we had a really good thing going
in the beginning.

00:18:34.551 --> 00:18:36.303
Yeah, you really did.

00:18:36.845 --> 00:18:38.555
I envied you guys back then.

00:18:47.314 --> 00:18:49.191
Seo Eun-ho, I must say,

00:18:49.775 --> 00:18:51.568
is not an easy one.

00:18:53.278 --> 00:18:56.782
You were super proactive when you were 20.

00:18:59.701 --> 00:19:01.203
Should I just go for it?

00:19:01.703 --> 00:19:04.039
Temples in classical architecture

00:19:04.122 --> 00:19:08.377
can be classified by the number of columns
in the front and rear facades.

00:19:09.169 --> 00:19:11.672
It's called "distyle"
when there are two columns,

00:19:11.755 --> 00:19:14.007
"tetrastyle" when there are four,

00:19:14.091 --> 00:19:16.885
and "hexastyle" when there are six.

00:19:17.386 --> 00:19:19.012
When it comes to the hexastyle…

00:19:31.942 --> 00:19:33.026
Hello.

00:19:33.527 --> 00:19:34.361
Hi.

00:19:34.945 --> 00:19:35.904
Can I sit here?

00:19:35.988 --> 00:19:37.364
Be my guest.

00:19:42.035 --> 00:19:42.869
Can you move over?

00:19:43.787 --> 00:19:44.871
Just a sec.

00:19:54.381 --> 00:19:55.674
Go ahead.

00:19:59.553 --> 00:20:01.471
So you're going to keep that up, huh?

00:20:03.307 --> 00:20:06.643
The columns of a temple can be classified
according to their forms…

00:20:06.727 --> 00:20:12.232
Since I decided to go for it,
I'm going to pull out all of my old moves.

00:20:15.861 --> 00:20:17.154
Where are we right now?

00:20:26.288 --> 00:20:27.748
Thank you!

00:20:39.509 --> 00:20:40.510
Sorry about that.

00:20:53.023 --> 00:20:53.857
Hey.

00:20:56.568 --> 00:20:57.402
Yes?

00:20:58.195 --> 00:20:59.571
Are you feeling unwell?

00:21:02.616 --> 00:21:03.450
No.

00:21:04.117 --> 00:21:04.951
Okay.

00:21:05.702 --> 00:21:07.245
Let's focus on the lecture.

00:21:19.925 --> 00:21:22.219
Eun-ho, you're off to practice,
aren't you?

00:21:22.719 --> 00:21:23.887
I'm going to the library.

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:27.182
Good. I was also on my way to the library.

00:21:27.265 --> 00:21:29.059
Come to think of it, I have practice.

00:21:30.936 --> 00:21:32.604
Me too. I have practice too.

00:22:00.090 --> 00:22:01.508
Should we get started first?

00:22:30.495 --> 00:22:31.413
What's he doing?

00:22:33.582 --> 00:22:34.541
Oh my God!

00:22:35.584 --> 00:22:36.668
Has he fallen for me?

00:22:54.227 --> 00:22:55.479
Don't you…

00:22:58.982 --> 00:23:00.400
go easy on me like last time.

00:23:05.155 --> 00:23:06.490
Give it everything you've got.

00:23:08.033 --> 00:23:08.867
This is bad.

00:23:12.078 --> 00:23:13.079
Put it on.

00:23:20.545 --> 00:23:23.089
I hurt his pride.

00:23:34.643 --> 00:23:36.144
Mi-rae, hi!

00:23:36.228 --> 00:23:37.771
Hello.

00:23:39.105 --> 00:23:40.106
What's going on?

00:23:40.774 --> 00:23:42.484
Did you two have a practice match?

00:23:43.777 --> 00:23:45.862
The thing is,

00:23:46.363 --> 00:23:47.280
Eun-ho…

00:23:47.364 --> 00:23:48.573
It was my idea.

00:23:53.411 --> 00:23:56.498
And? How did it go?

00:24:00.627 --> 00:24:02.128
MI-RAE, EUN-HO

00:24:02.212 --> 00:24:04.464
Wasn't I supposed to be a campus queen?

00:24:04.548 --> 00:24:06.716
They turned me into a full-on swordsman!

00:24:06.800 --> 00:24:08.385
WIN, LOSE

00:24:10.262 --> 00:24:11.471
No way.

00:24:11.972 --> 00:24:13.265
You lost?

00:24:16.268 --> 00:24:17.602
I don't believe it.

00:24:18.603 --> 00:24:19.437
Is it true?

00:24:22.816 --> 00:24:24.234
I'll go wash up.

00:24:36.371 --> 00:24:38.582
Let's go!

00:24:39.082 --> 00:24:41.459
Umchichi, umchichi, umchichi, umchichi!

00:24:41.543 --> 00:24:43.753
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!
-Carrot, carrot!

00:24:44.337 --> 00:24:48.174
It's been so long since I've felt
this excitement, this youthful energy!

00:24:48.258 --> 00:24:49.259
Carrot, carrot!

00:24:49.342 --> 00:24:50.802
Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!

00:24:50.885 --> 00:24:55.473
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!

00:24:55.557 --> 00:24:58.059
You got it wrong, Jung-pil! Drink up!

00:24:58.643 --> 00:25:00.061
Drink up!

00:25:00.145 --> 00:25:01.146
I'd like to

00:25:02.314 --> 00:25:03.315
take one for him.

00:25:05.233 --> 00:25:07.819
-Hey! Give us a penalty drink!
-Penalty!

00:25:07.902 --> 00:25:08.903
Okay!

00:25:09.613 --> 00:25:10.780
Here comes the drink.

00:25:10.864 --> 00:25:11.740
Mi-rae!

00:25:11.823 --> 00:25:13.867
-Mi-rae!
-All right, mix it up.

00:25:16.494 --> 00:25:17.537
Get ready.

00:25:20.915 --> 00:25:22.083
Even soju?

00:25:28.298 --> 00:25:30.550
All right. Here's your penalty drink.

00:25:31.926 --> 00:25:33.720
Mi-rae, just

00:25:35.263 --> 00:25:37.307
what kind of life have you had?

00:25:37.390 --> 00:25:40.310
I got carried away.

00:25:40.393 --> 00:25:41.895
Is that how you do it?

00:25:42.437 --> 00:25:43.688
Eun-ho!

00:25:43.772 --> 00:25:45.065
-Hello, Eun-ho.
-Eun-ho!

00:25:45.148 --> 00:25:46.691
-Hi, Eun-ho.
-Come sit down.

00:25:47.901 --> 00:25:49.986
-Sit here.
-Hello, Eun-ho.

00:25:50.612 --> 00:25:52.113
Why are you so late?

00:25:52.197 --> 00:25:53.448
-Assignment.
-Have a drink.

00:25:53.531 --> 00:25:55.784
Bottoms up! Yeah!

00:25:57.202 --> 00:25:58.370
Su-ji, that's enough.

00:25:59.537 --> 00:26:02.248
No. I know you're a lightweight.

00:26:02.332 --> 00:26:03.333
Cheers.

00:26:03.416 --> 00:26:04.626
I'll drink it.

00:26:05.877 --> 00:26:09.339
I knew I didn't like that girl
from the start.

00:26:09.839 --> 00:26:12.008
She oddly reminds me of Na You-mi.

00:26:12.509 --> 00:26:13.802
You have something on you.

00:26:14.969 --> 00:26:15.845
Jung-pil!

00:26:16.596 --> 00:26:18.390
No, don't push yourself!

00:26:18.890 --> 00:26:20.809
You're going to feel sick tomorrow.

00:26:21.893 --> 00:26:24.813
By the way, Mi-rae,
have you done any sports before?

00:26:26.523 --> 00:26:27.607
Not at all.

00:26:28.733 --> 00:26:30.151
Oh, you're an art major.

00:26:30.235 --> 00:26:33.613
A talented artist and a skilled athlete.
You've got it all!

00:26:35.782 --> 00:26:38.535
Please! You flatter me.

00:26:41.204 --> 00:26:43.248
Too much humility can hurt you, you know.

00:26:44.666 --> 00:26:46.126
What are you talking about?

00:26:46.626 --> 00:26:48.253
Being humble is a good thing.

00:26:48.753 --> 00:26:50.380
Eun-ho's right about that one.

00:26:50.463 --> 00:26:54.050
It can get a bit annoying
when someone takes it too far.

00:26:54.134 --> 00:26:54.968
Yup.

00:26:56.344 --> 00:26:57.429
Excuse me.

00:26:58.054 --> 00:26:59.097
What?

00:26:59.180 --> 00:27:00.098
Not you.

00:27:03.601 --> 00:27:04.602
Do you hate me?

00:27:07.147 --> 00:27:07.981
What?

00:27:12.610 --> 00:27:14.154
I don't hate people.

00:27:15.822 --> 00:27:17.073
Sorry if you felt that way.

00:27:21.453 --> 00:27:22.579
That's a relief.

00:27:24.581 --> 00:27:26.249
-Mi-rae?
-Mi-rae.

00:27:26.332 --> 00:27:27.792
Where are you going?

00:27:34.507 --> 00:27:36.926
Because I like you, Eun-ho.

00:27:38.887 --> 00:27:40.930
-What?
-I think she's drunk!

00:27:41.014 --> 00:27:43.725
-Come on!
-Stop cutting in line, Mi-rae!

00:27:48.730 --> 00:27:50.565
You know, we've just met.

00:27:51.399 --> 00:27:52.233
What?

00:27:53.318 --> 00:27:55.028
You don't know me that well.

00:28:01.534 --> 00:28:04.120
Kids nowadays sure are bold,
don't you think?

00:28:04.204 --> 00:28:06.539
Jung-pil, you've got some pie on you.

00:28:06.623 --> 00:28:07.874
Man, that's embarrassing!

00:28:07.957 --> 00:28:08.958
Cutie-pie.

00:28:10.084 --> 00:28:11.211
-So cute.
-Is she mad?

00:28:11.294 --> 00:28:12.420
Hold on.

00:28:13.213 --> 00:28:14.047
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

00:28:14.130 --> 00:28:15.965
-Sounds good, Jung-pil!
-Here you go!

00:28:18.426 --> 00:28:19.511
What the heck?

00:28:19.594 --> 00:28:20.762
You're the best.

00:28:20.845 --> 00:28:22.305
-See you. Bye!
-Bye-bye!

00:28:22.388 --> 00:28:24.140
-You want to get in this one?
-May I?

00:28:24.224 --> 00:28:25.308
Yeah. Get in.

00:28:25.892 --> 00:28:27.227
Thank you.

00:28:27.310 --> 00:28:28.812
You should get in too.

00:28:49.415 --> 00:28:50.291
Where are you going?

00:28:51.167 --> 00:28:52.043
To campus.

00:28:53.461 --> 00:28:54.963
Oh, you live in the dorm.

00:28:56.464 --> 00:28:57.924
Are you going to campus too?

00:28:58.007 --> 00:29:00.468
Yes, to the library
to finish my assignment.

00:29:09.811 --> 00:29:11.771
You might as well just walk next to me.

00:29:11.855 --> 00:29:14.023
I don't want to feel
like I'm being chased.

00:29:22.031 --> 00:29:23.700
-Eun-ho.
-What?

00:29:25.118 --> 00:29:26.536
Do you like the club president?

00:29:27.579 --> 00:29:28.413
What?

00:29:31.124 --> 00:29:32.625
Maybe that was too direct.

00:29:33.835 --> 00:29:35.587
Fine. Where is your hometown?

00:29:35.670 --> 00:29:38.298
What's your type?
Are you into video games and stuff?

00:29:38.923 --> 00:29:39.799
What's up with you?

00:29:41.217 --> 00:29:44.846
You said I barely know you.
I want to get to know you quickly.

00:29:55.189 --> 00:29:56.024
Eun-ho!

00:29:59.777 --> 00:30:00.862
Run!

00:30:58.753 --> 00:31:01.047
You can't go to the library
all soaked like that.

00:31:01.130 --> 00:31:03.341
I have dry clothes in my bag.

00:31:04.050 --> 00:31:05.718
You should dry them off a bit.

00:31:10.765 --> 00:31:11.683
LAUNDRY ROOM

00:31:13.309 --> 00:31:14.852
Someone's doing their job!

00:31:15.895 --> 00:31:17.647
I'm sure they'll dry off in a bit.

00:31:18.690 --> 00:31:19.774
Take care.

00:31:19.857 --> 00:31:20.942
Wait!

00:31:23.277 --> 00:31:25.863
There's a way we can dry your clothes.

00:31:42.922 --> 00:31:44.424
Thanks for letting me in here.

00:31:45.842 --> 00:31:47.844
This takes a while, doesn't it?

00:31:48.886 --> 00:31:49.804
Yeah.

00:31:54.100 --> 00:31:55.601
You should go change too.

00:31:59.480 --> 00:32:00.565
Don't want to.

00:32:02.650 --> 00:32:05.153
I want to stay here with you, Eun-ho.

00:32:14.037 --> 00:32:15.288
You're one of a kind.

00:32:20.334 --> 00:32:21.919
You're really bold, aren't you?

00:32:34.849 --> 00:32:37.852
I didn't see this coming.

00:32:42.106 --> 00:32:43.066
Se-june.

00:32:44.025 --> 00:32:45.818
Here. Eat up.

00:32:48.446 --> 00:32:50.990
Mi-rae, why are you so bold?

00:32:51.824 --> 00:32:52.658
What did I do?

00:32:54.452 --> 00:32:55.661
Do you like me?

00:32:56.621 --> 00:32:57.455
Yes.

00:33:12.303 --> 00:33:13.513
Why is this jerk

00:33:14.305 --> 00:33:16.349
suddenly invading my thoughts?

00:33:58.558 --> 00:33:59.559
Eun-ho.

00:34:25.209 --> 00:34:26.961
You'll catch a cold.

00:34:28.171 --> 00:34:29.005
Dry your hair.

00:34:33.926 --> 00:34:35.511
And I don't like her.

00:34:41.100 --> 00:34:44.020
I'll be in the reading room
while the laundry finishes. See you.

00:34:45.104 --> 00:34:46.272
Wait…

00:34:46.856 --> 00:34:48.149
Don't catch a cold.

00:35:12.215 --> 00:35:14.842
What was that? So annoying.

00:35:27.104 --> 00:35:30.107
General You-mi only lets me post
flattering photos of her.

00:35:30.191 --> 00:35:31.901
I'll let it slide since she's cute.

00:35:31.984 --> 00:35:33.736
Hashtag, soon to be taken.

00:35:37.782 --> 00:35:39.659
What's this? You posted a photo?

00:35:42.995 --> 00:35:44.664
What? I don't like this photo.

00:35:45.414 --> 00:35:46.249
You don't?

00:35:46.832 --> 00:35:49.502
No. You should have asked me first.

00:35:50.753 --> 00:35:52.213
Only you look good.

00:35:52.296 --> 00:35:55.633
I posted it because you told me to.
What's wrong with you?

00:35:57.510 --> 00:35:59.178
Why are you snapping at me?

00:35:59.262 --> 00:36:02.431
I only said that because you didn't have
any photos of us dating.

00:36:04.058 --> 00:36:06.435
Okay. Sorry. You want it down, is that it?

00:36:07.979 --> 00:36:09.188
Never mind. Just leave it.

00:36:20.825 --> 00:36:22.827
BLOCK

00:36:47.601 --> 00:36:49.228
I'm doing fine too, you know.

00:36:52.732 --> 00:36:53.899
I'm happy too.

00:37:09.540 --> 00:37:13.836
Then again, there's no rule saying
I have to be doing fine in the real world.

00:37:49.997 --> 00:37:51.332
Let's go eat.

00:37:55.795 --> 00:37:57.046
Okay, Eun-ho!

00:37:57.880 --> 00:38:00.257
I heard the architecture program
is super hard.

00:38:00.341 --> 00:38:02.426
Jung-pil told me that, by the third year,

00:38:02.510 --> 00:38:05.096
your blood is basically coffee
from all the all-nighters.

00:38:06.222 --> 00:38:09.266
But I don't think
I've ever seen you drink coffee.

00:38:09.350 --> 00:38:10.393
Don't you like coffee?

00:38:10.476 --> 00:38:12.770
Oh, I'm guessing
caffeine doesn't agree with you.

00:38:13.521 --> 00:38:15.356
Want to go to a café after this?

00:38:17.233 --> 00:38:19.360
Love it. I like lattes.

00:38:19.443 --> 00:38:20.694
You like lattes?

00:38:41.424 --> 00:38:42.675
All done.

00:38:43.342 --> 00:38:44.176
What do you think?

00:38:44.760 --> 00:38:45.761
You nailed it.

00:39:07.491 --> 00:39:10.703
Like trying to paint over
old memories with new ones…

00:39:19.295 --> 00:39:21.547
I immersed myself in Boyfriend on Demand.

00:39:28.387 --> 00:39:29.513
Eun-ho.

00:39:33.350 --> 00:39:34.518
How did it go?

00:39:35.394 --> 00:39:36.395
The exam?

00:39:36.479 --> 00:39:37.897
I blew it.

00:39:43.110 --> 00:39:44.028
Because of you.

00:39:56.957 --> 00:40:00.753
Is it true that a kumdo practitioner
could beat anyone with just chopsticks?

00:40:01.378 --> 00:40:03.172
-Drinking game?
-Let's go!

00:40:04.381 --> 00:40:05.257
Bunny bunny?

00:40:05.758 --> 00:40:07.635
Not even. Don't be ridiculous.

00:40:08.260 --> 00:40:10.471
Why not? You can stab people with them.

00:40:10.554 --> 00:40:13.390
-Aim for the vital spots.
-Bunny, bunny! Carrot, carrot!

00:40:13.474 --> 00:40:14.308
Stab!

00:40:14.391 --> 00:40:15.976
Carrot, carrot!

00:40:16.644 --> 00:40:18.896
No thrusts allowed until you're third dan.

00:40:18.979 --> 00:40:20.022
Why?

00:40:22.441 --> 00:40:24.485
Why are you outside by yourself?

00:40:27.780 --> 00:40:29.281
Can I ask you something?

00:40:31.408 --> 00:40:32.243
Sure.

00:40:33.953 --> 00:40:35.412
To you, am I still…

00:40:39.083 --> 00:40:40.417
just an upperclassman?

00:40:47.341 --> 00:40:48.759
Why did I quit being an author?

00:40:48.842 --> 00:40:50.928
Kim Baek-chun, the author, said to me,

00:40:51.011 --> 00:40:53.264
"Hey, kid, you should give up
on being an author."

00:40:53.347 --> 00:40:57.142
That's why I quit.
That's how tight we are.

00:40:57.226 --> 00:40:58.352
What's wrong with you?

00:40:58.435 --> 00:40:59.937
Wow, you're indebted to him.

00:41:01.021 --> 00:41:03.524
-What was that?
-You're indebted to him. Indebted.

00:41:07.236 --> 00:41:09.989
What? There wasn't any rain
in the forecast.

00:41:22.543 --> 00:41:24.878
You came to a company dinner.
How unlike you.

00:41:25.379 --> 00:41:28.465
Yeah, it felt kind of awkward
to go home for dinner.

00:41:29.133 --> 00:41:29.967
I see.

00:41:32.011 --> 00:41:33.095
Are you heading home?

00:41:33.178 --> 00:41:34.305
Yes, I am

00:41:35.431 --> 00:41:36.432
not.

00:41:37.266 --> 00:41:38.309
You're not going home?

00:41:39.393 --> 00:41:41.604
-Then back to the office?
-Seriously?

00:41:42.104 --> 00:41:44.106
Does he think I have nowhere else to be?

00:41:44.189 --> 00:41:46.942
Oh, well, I have a date, you see.

00:41:49.778 --> 00:41:50.613
I see.

00:42:00.748 --> 00:42:01.874
He'll be picking you up?

00:42:02.875 --> 00:42:03.709
Yes.

00:42:04.835 --> 00:42:06.003
Enjoy your date, then.

00:42:13.135 --> 00:42:15.346
A date, really? Have you lost it?

00:42:35.991 --> 00:42:36.992
I'm freezing.

00:42:56.095 --> 00:42:57.638
VISUAL DESIGN CLASS GROUP CHAT
NA YOU-MI

00:42:57.721 --> 00:43:00.265
Here is our mobile wedding invitation.

00:43:00.349 --> 00:43:02.935
You are cordially invited
to Se-june and You-mi's wedding!

00:43:03.018 --> 00:43:05.062
MOBILE WEDDING INVITATION

00:43:06.021 --> 00:43:08.691
SUNDAY, NOVEMBER 23, 2025
KIM SE-JUNE, NA YOU-MI

00:43:13.862 --> 00:43:18.158
Oh my God, you two look great together!
Congratulations, You-mi and Se-june.

00:43:18.242 --> 00:43:20.703
You-mi, you look so pretty.

00:43:20.786 --> 00:43:23.038
You'd better treat her well, Se-june.

00:43:23.330 --> 00:43:24.164
JI-YEON

00:43:24.248 --> 00:43:27.584
Is she out of her mind?
She totally knew you were in this chat.

00:43:53.110 --> 00:43:54.153
Hello.

00:43:55.612 --> 00:43:57.448
It's me. Did you have my number?

00:43:59.700 --> 00:44:00.617
No.

00:44:02.870 --> 00:44:04.538
At least you recognized my voice.

00:44:05.622 --> 00:44:06.540
Why did you call?

00:44:08.333 --> 00:44:11.378
Well, it's just, You-mi…

00:44:13.005 --> 00:44:15.841
Damn, the thing she posted on the chat
is bothering me.

00:44:16.592 --> 00:44:17.551
Did you see it?

00:44:20.179 --> 00:44:21.013
Yeah.

00:44:22.014 --> 00:44:23.223
You guys look happy.

00:44:24.266 --> 00:44:25.225
I'm sorry.

00:44:29.313 --> 00:44:30.314
About what?

00:44:31.607 --> 00:44:33.025
For making you see that.

00:44:34.693 --> 00:44:35.527
It…

00:44:36.862 --> 00:44:39.531
It wasn't so different
from any other invitation.

00:44:44.870 --> 00:44:47.372
Right. I'm glad you're okay with it.

00:44:48.499 --> 00:44:49.374
Yeah.

00:44:54.505 --> 00:44:56.590
I'm hanging up now. Take care.

00:45:01.762 --> 00:45:02.721
Yeah.

00:45:29.414 --> 00:45:31.250
NOTIFICATION

00:45:35.295 --> 00:45:40.592
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, four hours remain
until your subscription expires.

00:45:42.928 --> 00:45:44.263
Today, of all days?

00:46:01.488 --> 00:46:05.075
I'm so sorry, but I love you
It's all a lie

00:46:05.158 --> 00:46:09.913
I had no idea, I finally get it
I need you

00:46:09.997 --> 00:46:13.000
Sorry, but I love you
Those piercing words

00:46:13.083 --> 00:46:17.212
In the heat of the moment
I ended up letting you go

00:46:17.296 --> 00:46:20.382
I'm so sorry, but I love you
It's all a lie

00:46:20.465 --> 00:46:21.466
Together now!

00:46:27.973 --> 00:46:30.225
Mi-rae.

00:46:32.311 --> 00:46:33.854
You can't just walk away like that.

00:46:34.521 --> 00:46:37.065
I did because you were talking nonsense.

00:46:37.149 --> 00:46:38.775
-Let go.
-I can't.

00:46:38.859 --> 00:46:40.903
If I let go, you'll just leave,

00:46:41.528 --> 00:46:45.032
and you'll blame yourself
for letting our last moment end like this.

00:46:45.115 --> 00:46:47.451
I'll deal with it myself. Let me go.

00:46:48.327 --> 00:46:49.620
I said let go!

00:46:52.331 --> 00:46:53.165
Why?

00:46:54.082 --> 00:46:56.460
You broke up with me.
Why won't you let me leave?

00:46:57.544 --> 00:46:58.754
Who do you think you are?

00:46:59.546 --> 00:47:01.214
Just who do you think you are?

00:47:12.976 --> 00:47:16.939
I may have brought it up first,
but we both already knew

00:47:18.065 --> 00:47:19.441
that things had changed.

00:47:21.443 --> 00:47:23.028
That's what you think.

00:47:23.779 --> 00:47:25.072
I never changed.

00:47:26.281 --> 00:47:27.115
Mi-rae.

00:47:29.409 --> 00:47:30.911
We all change.

00:47:33.330 --> 00:47:34.748
You've also changed.

00:47:36.708 --> 00:47:38.543
If I can love you

00:47:39.461 --> 00:47:41.630
for who you've become,

00:47:42.673 --> 00:47:44.800
that would mean
we can be together forever.

00:47:46.760 --> 00:47:47.886
But I…

00:47:50.639 --> 00:47:53.016
I'm not sure if I can do that with you.

00:48:51.241 --> 00:48:53.368
-Wow, look.
-It's beautiful.

00:48:53.452 --> 00:48:54.786
-What is this place?
-Amazing.

00:49:01.168 --> 00:49:03.128
-Let's take pictures.
-It's lovely.

00:49:09.009 --> 00:49:10.177
Is something wrong?

00:49:24.566 --> 00:49:26.526
I don't know what's going on,

00:49:28.028 --> 00:49:31.406
but get some sleep
and just clear your mind.

00:50:05.607 --> 00:50:06.817
You know what?

00:50:07.442 --> 00:50:08.610
Ever since we broke up,

00:50:09.194 --> 00:50:13.365
I've never once thought back
to our early days together.

00:50:50.527 --> 00:50:52.404
-Cheers!
-Finish it off!

00:51:10.088 --> 00:51:11.715
Se-june!

00:51:28.106 --> 00:51:29.524
SEO MI-RAE

00:51:31.651 --> 00:51:32.736
Don't I look good?

00:51:34.196 --> 00:51:35.697
For your first day at work.

00:51:37.199 --> 00:51:38.033
Thanks!

00:51:59.638 --> 00:52:00.555
Got some sleep?

00:52:01.473 --> 00:52:03.058
You had a long day.

00:52:06.186 --> 00:52:09.064
Because you had changed anyway.

00:52:09.564 --> 00:52:11.399
Because we were over anyway.

00:52:12.442 --> 00:52:15.111
Because I hated your guts so much.

00:52:18.490 --> 00:52:19.574
But

00:52:20.408 --> 00:52:23.745
being in here brought the memories back,
and strangely…

00:52:29.668 --> 00:52:30.919
I don't hate you now.

00:52:37.801 --> 00:52:44.099
HANSAE KUMDO CLUB
FRESHMAN WELCOME TRIP

00:52:51.815 --> 00:52:53.608
We're here. Let's get off.

00:53:10.041 --> 00:53:10.875
Over there.

00:53:12.460 --> 00:53:13.753
It's a shooting star.

00:53:17.090 --> 00:53:18.216
Want to see it up close?

00:53:22.804 --> 00:53:24.222
Is there something here?

00:53:24.723 --> 00:53:25.890
You'll see.

00:54:04.637 --> 00:54:05.555
Eun-ho.

00:54:09.309 --> 00:54:10.810
Do you like me now?

00:54:15.982 --> 00:54:17.192
Still not there yet?

00:54:35.251 --> 00:54:36.586
Eun-ho.

00:54:39.005 --> 00:54:41.466
If you end up marrying
someone other than me,

00:54:42.300 --> 00:54:43.968
will you forget about me?

00:54:45.345 --> 00:54:46.554
What do you mean?

00:54:52.602 --> 00:54:55.605
It's not like you lose your memories
when you marry someone.

00:54:55.688 --> 00:54:57.399
I'm sure I'll remember everything.

00:54:59.275 --> 00:55:00.693
My heart may forget…

00:55:02.695 --> 00:55:04.280
but the memories will remain.

00:55:08.118 --> 00:55:10.036
How will you remember me?

00:55:14.707 --> 00:55:16.167
The way I was in the end?

00:55:17.877 --> 00:55:18.878
Or

00:55:20.380 --> 00:55:21.673
in the beginning?

00:55:22.924 --> 00:55:24.342
It's all you.

00:55:27.595 --> 00:55:28.930
I'll remember it all.

00:55:31.015 --> 00:55:31.891
The beginning…

00:55:33.977 --> 00:55:34.894
and the end.

00:55:43.528 --> 00:55:44.446
Okay.

00:55:45.947 --> 00:55:47.365
That will do.

00:56:18.062 --> 00:56:19.230
Have a good life.

00:56:22.484 --> 00:56:23.359
You too.

00:56:45.548 --> 00:56:47.634
You sound like you're about to go away.

00:56:55.016 --> 00:56:56.017
You must be cold.

01:00:38.823 --> 01:00:43.828
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon